message.body: I am selling your tires tomorrow night (I just sold mine tonight!). How much are they going for?
Also, dinner at Chiro and Melinda's was out of this world: sukiyaki, tons of sake, sashimi, dumplings, local kimchi, Japanese whisky. Yum!
Sounds amazing, tires for $150, did anyone get in touch about the bass?
Yeah, bass was listed as 550, guys name is steve
But I found out I'm working an afternoon party at 1 pm at the Blue Cat. Sorry we won't be able to hang out in the afternoon.
I can cancel it if you are coming up early in the day.
I wasnt planning on coming up that early, you should work
Ok thanks baby. The guy is coming to look at the bass in a second. I will let you know how it goes.
He checked over the bass and loved it, but he wants to talk to you first. Not sure if he has questions.
He just left, but he said he will call you.
Is he still there? Have him call me
